270
00:15:02,525 --> 00:15:04,295
Don't you know what prohibited means?

271
00:15:05,025 --> 00:15:06,665
I told you not to come up here.

272
00:15:08,265 --> 00:15:10,333
No one is helping the minority shareholders...

273
00:15:10,334 --> 00:15:12,364
of People's Entertainment who have done nothing wrong.

274
00:15:12,864 --> 00:15:14,133
But so many people are helping him,

275
00:15:14,134 --> 00:15:15,905
even though he's done so many bad things.

276
00:15:18,035 --> 00:15:19,244
It's unfair.

277
00:15:39,395 --> 00:15:42,634
An accountant's role and responsibility...

278
00:15:42,864 --> 00:15:45,435
is not for people who work for their money.

279
00:15:45,604 --> 00:15:48,305
