294
00:16:37,254 --> 00:16:39,285
so that she wouldn't worry.

295
00:16:45,765 --> 00:16:48,765
It's only been a few months since I opened this restaurant,

296
00:16:49,364 --> 00:16:53,104
but it's already turning into a place for accountants.

297
00:16:53,665 --> 00:16:55,774
This apparently used to be...

298
00:16:55,775 --> 00:16:59,505
their clubhouse or something.

299
00:17:00,874 --> 00:17:05,215
I'm worried about running into people from my firm here.

300
00:17:07,114 --> 00:17:10,214
I don't want to tell them for the time being.

301
00:17:10,215 --> 00:17:12,154
Why do you need to tell them?

302
00:17:12,854 --> 00:17:15,854
Whenever I see that arrogant professor,

303
00:17:17,495 --> 00:17:19,764
I'm dying to tell him...

304
00:17:19,765 --> 00:17:21,833
that my grandson is an accountant.

305
00:17:21,834 --> 00:17:23,864
But I've held back until now.

306
00:17:31,334 --> 00:17:33,045
One gukbap, please.

307
00:17:33,545 --> 00:17:35,344
Yes. Take a seat.

308
00:17:51,194 --> 00:17:52,525
Ho Woo. What's wrong?

309
00:17:53,424 --> 00:17:58,035
