314
00:18:23,725 --> 00:18:24,824
Hello?

315
00:18:24,825 --> 00:18:25,995
Ms. Jin.

316
00:18:26,094 --> 00:18:27,325
Are you working on something lately?

317
00:18:28,434 --> 00:18:30,664
I was.

318
00:18:30,694 --> 00:18:31,864
