00:21:16,295 --> 00:21:17,295
Yes.

370
00:21:21,975 --> 00:21:23,275
There is a way.

371
00:21:23,604 --> 00:21:24,674
Jang Ho Woo.

372
00:21:28,045 --> 00:21:31,515
I know how we can persuade Jisan Bank.

