00:21:38,755 --> 00:21:41,025
Do you know the term "wag the dog?"

375
00:21:42,225 --> 00:21:43,325
"Wag the dog?"

376
00:21:43,924 --> 00:21:45,524
You move the tail...

377
00:21:45,525 --> 00:21:48,694
